eig= get_eigenvalue(peliculas.ca)
traza= sum(eig[1:2])
chi2 = traza*sum(as.matrix(peliculas)) 
chi2
## [1] 231.3889
gdl=(nrow(peliculas) - 1) * (ncol(peliculas) - 1)
gdl #8 GRADOS DE LIBERTAD
## [1] 8
p.val = pchisq(chi2, df = gdl, lower.tail = FALSE)
